Description: Dear Sir/Madam,

I submit this ticket on behalf of Huawei.

Currently, entities such as users and computers cannot be exported. There is no response after the Export button is clicked. The prompt shows the potential reason of this problem is low space disks. Please refer to the attached screenshots.

Until Feb 15, the system runs well.

Please help Huawei solve this problem. Thanks a lot in advance. (I prefer Adrian handle this ticket. He is always in charge of Huawei's case).
